00:52:40.910 --> 00:52:41.910
Celsius and lo and behold next year it was
cool by half a degree Celsius; there was more

00:52:41.910 --> 00:52:42.910
ice in the Arctic which meant more polar bears
and the biologists called the cubs Mt. Pinatubo

00:52:42.910 --> 00:52:43.910
cubs.

00:52:43.910 --> 00:52:44.910
So this is the one that the climatologists
think, "Well, if volcanoes can do it, we can

00:52:44.910 --> 00:52:45.910
do it." And of course Nathan and the intellectual
ventures guy wanted to, guys wanted to get

